{"tid":1804213,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"嘩，羅鈞滿北上r撈失敗，變到成個北佬咁","createTime":"2019-12-30T23:40:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T02:52:00.000Z","uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2a0acd298c0cc446ad105c24d370fc68c9dde9df","tid":1804213,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T23:40:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/os_feat_1150_moon_4808767915dfe4bd14799a-1050x631.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2Fos_feat_1150_moon_4808767915dfe4bd14799a-1050x631.jpg&h=8794851b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近年唔少藝人離開無綫北上，希望闖出一片天，羅鈞滿就係其中一員，不過佢無其他人咁好彩，3年嚟發展平平，上個月回流返港簽約新公司，不過就未有工開，無見一排佬味重咗，唔知之後會做咩角色呢？<br />\n撰文、圖片：東方新地<br />\n<br />\n羅鈞滿北上闖蕩未如理想回流返港無工開<br />\n<br />\n2016年約滿無綫北上闖蕩，3年來羅鈞滿都拍過幾套內地劇同網絡電影，可惜回響不如預期，原來人仔都唔係想像中咁易賺。好彩兜兜轉轉上月宣布簽約邵氏成為旗 下藝人，不過就未見佢有新工作動向公布住，除咗遊山玩水接連出埠旅行，仲見到佢好得閒咁一支公喺尖沙咀出現。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/e_1150a_aunt_pxx_15505304065dfe48774387e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2Fe_1150a_aunt_pxx_15505304065dfe48774387e.jpg&h=36e2775e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n北上浸淫3年35歲仔現北方同胞味<br />\n<br />\n35歲仔，北上一輪佬味重咗，腋下挾住個袋帶點北方同胞味，著上白色上衣襯 睡褲款間條長褲，但又無喇喇搭對啡色牛津皮鞋。呢身造型嚟講，只能夠講句，fashion嘅嘢八姨太識條鐵咩？<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/f_1150a_aunt_pxx_13242041175dfe48783c59f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2Ff_1150a_aunt_pxx_13242041175dfe48783c59f.jpg&h=76506b12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/g_1150a_aunt_pxx_5574479695dfe487949373.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2Fg_1150a_aunt_pxx_5574479695dfe487949373.jpg&h=6cd4bad9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dbfd4fde7c9cdd6dcfe14b1ebe956a025c423380","tid":1804213,"uid":5649,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T23:42:25.000Z","msg":"有幾廢先會以香港人身分喺大陸撈唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25112bdcaee8a8f29a76d473be66c4f7f3aa7421","tid":1804213,"uid":335235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T23:44:35.000Z","msg":"who f. care?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"799512323c597f21b273ba8f3156ef2beff069f1","tid":1804213,"uid":181549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T23:45:31.000Z","msg":"抵死"},{"pid":"dbba56d0042ff38ea779a73351e741ec935d8cae","tid":1804213,"uid":333741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T23:53:19.000Z","msg":"本身都吾令仔 整完容仲樣衰左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6f26e1be2e9c4dbe8983ccf2eb7e74c3a370bf1","tid":1804213,"uid":102078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:25:37.000Z","msg":"Old news"},{"pid":"687475cd7cb99ecb7e2f1e0db232ef76c6be006f","tid":1804213,"uid":327462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:35:52.000Z","msg":"支那狗躝返上去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返黎香港做乜春呀"},{"pid":"ee52de97ccbd36edf1308d97a9bb822c3c4f12c3","tid":1804213,"uid":53187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T04:32:49.000Z","msg":"仲樣衰過的士陳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc9fafe8202aa75f29d2baf5cab3c8f59e2d3a6b","tid":1804213,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:30:25.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"8216118e02e1f4e5ad80c649d9b6f86f75a4daeb","tid":1804213,"uid":196814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T02:52:00.000Z","msg":"睇第三張圖 心諗都唔係呀揸法拉利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}